lessons.content:
State 多 / 複雜時、useState 變亂—useReducer 是內建解法。


### useState vs useReducer

```text
useState：
- 適合：簡單 state（boolean / number / string / 1-2 個 object 欄位）
- 多個 setter
- 改邏輯散落

useReducer：
- 適合：複雜 state（多欄位 + 多 action）
- 1 個 dispatch
- 改邏輯集中

何時用 useReducer：
1. State 是物件、5+ 欄位
2. 多種 action（add / remove / update / reset）
3. Action 之間有依賴
4. Logic 複雜（驗證、計算）
```


### 基本 useReducer

```tsx
// State 型別
interface State {
    count: number;
    step: number;
}

// Action 型別（discriminated union）
type Action =
    | { type: "increment" }
    | { type: "decrement" }
    | { type: "reset" }
    | { type: "setStep"; step: number };

// Reducer：(state, action) => newState
function reducer(state: State, action: Action): State {
    switch (action.type) {
        case "increment":
            return { ...state, count: state.count + state.step };
        case "decrement":
            return { ...state, count: state.count - state.step };
        case "reset":
            return { count: 0, step: 1 };
        case "setStep":
            return { ...state, step: action.step };
    }
}

// Component
function Counter() {
    const [state, dispatch] = useReducer(reducer, {
        count: 0,
        step: 1
    });

    return (
        <div>
            <p>Count: {state.count}</p>
            <p>Step: {state.step}</p>
            <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "increment" })}>+</button>
            <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "decrement" })}>-</button>
            <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "reset" })}>Reset</button>
            <input
                type="number"
                value={state.step}
                onChange={(e) => dispatch({
                    type: "setStep",
                    step: +e.target.value
                })}
            />
        </div>
    );
}
```


### 實戰：Todo Reducer

```tsx
interface Todo {
    id: number;
    text: string;
    done: boolean;
}

interface State {
    todos: Todo[];
    filter: "all" | "active" | "done";
}

type Action =
    | { type: "add"; text: string }
    | { type: "toggle"; id: number }
    | { type: "delete"; id: number }
    | { type: "edit"; id: number; text: string }
    | { type: "setFilter"; filter: State["filter"] }
    | { type: "clearDone" };

function reducer(state: State, action: Action): State {
    switch (action.type) {
        case "add":
            return {
                ...state,
                todos: [...state.todos, {
                    id: Date.now(),
                    text: action.text,
                    done: false
                }]
            };
        case "toggle":
            return {
                ...state,
                todos: state.todos.map(t =>
                    t.id === action.id ? { ...t, done: !t.done } : t
                )
            };
        case "delete":
            return {
                ...state,
                todos: state.todos.filter(t => t.id !== action.id)
            };
        case "edit":
            return {
                ...state,
                todos: state.todos.map(t =>
                    t.id === action.id ? { ...t, text: action.text } : t
                )
            };
        case "setFilter":
            return { ...state, filter: action.filter };
        case "clearDone":
            return {
                ...state,
                todos: state.todos.filter(t => !t.done)
            };
    }
}

function TodoApp() {
    const [state, dispatch] = useReducer(reducer, {
        todos: [],
        filter: "all"
    });

    const visibleTodos = state.todos.filter(t => {
        if (state.filter === "active") return !t.done;
        if (state.filter === "done") return t.done;
        return true;
    });

    return (
        <div>
            <input
                onKeyDown={(e) => {
                    if (e.key === "Enter") {
                        dispatch({ type: "add", text: e.currentTarget.value });
                        e.currentTarget.value = "";
                    }
                }}
            />

            <ul>
                {visibleTodos.map(todo => (
                    <li key={todo.id}>
                        <input
                            type="checkbox"
                            checked={todo.done}
                            onChange={() => dispatch({ type: "toggle", id: todo.id })}
                        />
                        <span>{todo.text}</span>
                        <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "delete", id: todo.id })}>
                            ×
                        </button>
                    </li>
                ))}
            </ul>

            <div>
                <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "setFilter", filter: "all" })}>All</button>
                <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "setFilter", filter: "active" })}>Active</button>
                <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "setFilter", filter: "done" })}>Done</button>
                <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "clearDone" })}>Clear Done</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    );
}
```


### Reducer + Context（mini Redux）

```tsx
// 大專案：reducer + context
// 不用 Redux 也能做

import { createContext, useContext, useReducer, ReactNode, Dispatch } from "react";

const StateContext = createContext<State | null>(null);
const DispatchContext = createContext<Dispatch<Action> | null>(null);

export function StoreProvider({ children }: { children: ReactNode }) {
    const [state, dispatch] = useReducer(reducer, initialState);

    return (
        <StateContext.Provider value={state}>
            <DispatchContext.Provider value={dispatch}>
                {children}
            </DispatchContext.Provider>
        </StateContext.Provider>
    );
}

// 分開 hook（性能）
export function useStoreState() {
    const state = useContext(StateContext);
    if (!state) throw new Error("Need StoreProvider");
    return state;
}

export function useStoreDispatch() {
    const dispatch = useContext(DispatchContext);
    if (!dispatch) throw new Error("Need StoreProvider");
    return dispatch;
}

// 用
function Component() {
    const state = useStoreState();
    const dispatch = useStoreDispatch();

    return (
        <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: "increment" })}>
            {state.count}
        </button>
    );
}

// dispatch 永遠同 reference、訂閱 dispatch 的不會 re-render
// state 變才 re-render 對應 component
```


### 進階：Immer 簡化

```tsx
import { produce } from "immer";

// 不用 spread、直接寫
function reducer(state: State, action: Action): State {
    return produce(state, draft => {
        switch (action.type) {
            case "add":
                draft.todos.push({
                    id: Date.now(),
                    text: action.text,
                    done: false
                });
                break;
            case "toggle":
                const todo = draft.todos.find(t => t.id === action.id);
                if (todo) todo.done = !todo.done;
                break;
            case "delete":
                draft.todos = draft.todos.filter(t => t.id !== action.id);
                break;
        }
    });
}

// 比 spread 直觀
// Immer 內部處理 immutable
```


### 什麼時候不用 useReducer？

```text
不該用 useReducer：

1. 簡單 state
   ❌ const [count, dispatch] = useReducer(...);
   ✓ const [count, setCount] = useState(0);

2. Server data
   ✓ React Query（自動 cache、refetch）
   ✗ useReducer + 手動 fetch

3. Form state
   ✓ React Hook Form
   ✗ useReducer + 手動 input

4. 全域複雜 state
   ✓ Zustand / Jotai（簡單）
   ✓ Redux Toolkit（完整 ecosystem）

useReducer 甜蜜點：
- Component 內複雜 state
- 5+ actions
- 中等規模
- 不要全域
```


### 2026 替代方案

```text
useReducer 適合場景越來越窄：

組件內複雜 state → useReducer ✓
組件間 state → useContext + useReducer 或 Zustand
全域 state → Zustand / Jotai
Server state → React Query / SWR
Form state → React Hook Form
URL state → Next Router / TanStack Router

業界 2026 趨勢：
- Zustand 取代部分 useReducer
- 但 useReducer 仍是 component 內複雜邏輯首選
- 不被取代
```


**☕ 用人話講**

useReducer 4 心法：(1) **state 複雜時用**—多欄位、多 action (2) **action 用 discriminated union**—type-safe (3) **spread 保持 immutable**—或用 Immer (4) **Reducer + Context = mini Redux**。**2026 業界**：複雜 component state 用 useReducer、全域 state 用 Zustand。

