React 預設「過度 re-render」—學完這節知道何時優化、怎麼優化。


### 什麼造成性能問題

```text
1. 過度 re-render
   - 父 re-render → 子全 re-render
2. 大計算 - filter / sort 1 萬個 item
3. 大 list 一次渲染 - 1000 個 DOM 卡頓
4. Bundle 太大 - 首屏 JS 5MB
5. Re-mount 太多 - key 改了 state 重來
```


### 診斷工具

```text
1. React DevTools Profiler（Chrome extension）
2. Chrome Performance tab
3. Lighthouse
4. why-did-you-render（lib）
5. React 19 內建工具
```


### 3 個優化 hook

```tsx
// 1. useMemo：cache 計算結果
const filtered = useMemo(() => {
    return items.filter(i => i.name.includes(query));
}, [items, query]);

// 2. useCallback：cache function
const handleClick = useCallback(() => {
    console.log("click");
}, []);

// 3. React.memo：cache component
const Child = React.memo(function Child({ name }) {
    return {name};
});

// 3 個搭配：
const Child = React.memo(function Child({ items, onSelect }) {
    return ...;
});

function Parent() {
    const [count, setCount] = useState(0);

    const items = useMemo(() => computeItems(), []);
    const handleSelect = useCallback((id) => { ... }, []);

    return (
        <>
             setCount(c => c + 1)}>{count}


    );
}
```


### 不要過度優化

```text
2026 共識：80% 場景不該手動 memo

什麼時候真要優化？
✓ Profiler 顯示 specific component 慢
✓ 大 list（1000+ items）
✓ Expensive 計算
✓ Heavy component（chart / editor）

什麼時候不要？
✗ 小 component 沒性能問題
✗ 簡單算
✗ 沒測量過、瞎猜慢
```


### Code Splitting

```tsx
import { lazy, Suspense } from "react";
import { Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom";

// Route-level
const Home = lazy(() => import("./pages/Home"));
const Dashboard = lazy(() => import("./pages/Dashboard"));

function App() {
    return (
        <Routes>
            <Route path="/" element={
                <Suspense fallback={<Spinner />}>
                    <Home />
                </Suspense>
            } />
            <Route path="/dashboard" element={
                <Suspense fallback={<Spinner />}>
                    <Dashboard />
                </Suspense>
            } />
        </Routes>
    );
}

// Component-level（heavy component）
const HeavyChart = lazy(() => import("./HeavyChart"));

// Library splitting
import debounce from "lodash/debounce";   // 只 import debounce
// 不要：import { debounce } from "lodash";（整包都拉進來）

// Next.js 自動 route-level splitting
```


### 大 list：Virtual Scrolling

```tsx
import { useVirtualizer } from "@tanstack/react-virtual";
import { useRef } from "react";

function VirtualList({ items }) {
    const parentRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);

    const virtualizer = useVirtualizer({
        count: items.length,
        getScrollElement: () => parentRef.current,
        estimateSize: () => 50
    });

    return (
        <div ref={parentRef} style={{ height: 400, overflow: "auto" }}>
            <div style={{ height: virtualizer.getTotalSize(), position: "relative" }}>
                {virtualizer.getVirtualItems().map(virtualItem => (
                    <div
                        key={virtualItem.key}
                        style={{
                            position: "absolute",
                            top: 0,
                            transform: `translateY(${virtualItem.start}px)`
                        }}
                    >
                        {items[virtualItem.index].name}
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </div>
    );
}

// 1 萬個 item 也順（只渲染畫面內看得到的）
```


### Image 優化

```tsx
// Next.js Image（自動）
