React 元件測試 2026 主流：**Vitest + React Testing Library**。


### 測試工具選擇


|  | Vitest | Jest | Bun test |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 速度 | 最快 | 慢 | 最快 |
| ESM 支援 | 原生 | 需設定 | 原生 |
| 2026 主流 | 新專案首選 | 老專案 | 實驗 |


### 裝 + 設定

```bash
$ npm install -D vitest @testing-library/react @testing-library/jest-dom @testing-library/user-event jsdom
```

```ts
// vitest.config.ts
import { defineConfig } from "vitest/config";
import react from "@vitejs/plugin-react";

export default defineConfig({
    plugins: [react()],
    test: {
        environment: "jsdom",
        globals: true,
        setupFiles: "./test/setup.ts"
    }
});

// test/setup.ts
import "@testing-library/jest-dom";

// package.json
{
    "scripts": {
        "test": "vitest",
        "test:ui": "vitest --ui",
        "test:coverage": "vitest --coverage"
    }
}
```


### 第一個 test

```tsx
// Counter.tsx
function Counter() {
    const [count, setCount] = useState(0);
    return (
        <div>
            <p>Count: {count}</p>
            <button onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}>+</button>
        </div>
    );
}

// Counter.test.tsx
import { render, screen } from "@testing-library/react";
import userEvent from "@testing-library/user-event";
import { describe, it, expect } from "vitest";

describe("Counter", () => {
    it("renders count 0 initially", () => {
        render(<Counter />);
        expect(screen.getByText("Count: 0")).toBeInTheDocument();
    });

    it("increments on click", async () => {
        const user = userEvent.setup();
        render(<Counter />);

        const button = screen.getByRole("button", { name: "+" });
        await user.click(button);

        expect(screen.getByText("Count: 1")).toBeInTheDocument();
    });
});

// 跑測試：npm test
```


### Testing Library 哲學

```text
「Test like a user uses it」

不要：
❌ 測 internal state
❌ 用 className / data-testid（除非必要）

要：
✓ 測用戶看到的（screen.getByText）
✓ 測用戶能做的（user.click）
✓ 用 accessibility（getByRole）

Query 順序：
1. getByRole（最 accessible）
2. getByLabelText
3. getByText
4. getByDisplayValue
5. getByTestId（最後選擇）
```


### 常見 test patterns

```tsx
// 1. Form test
it("submits with valid input", async () => {
    const user = userEvent.setup();
    const onSubmit = vi.fn();

    render(<LoginForm onSubmit={onSubmit} />);

    await user.type(screen.getByLabelText("Email"), "alice@x.com");
    await user.type(screen.getByLabelText("Password"), "password123");
    await user.click(screen.getByRole("button", { name: "Login" }));

    expect(onSubmit).toHaveBeenCalledWith({
        email: "alice@x.com",
        password: "password123"
    });
});

// 2. Async test（findBy 自動等）
it("loads users", async () => {
    render(<UserList />);
    const alice = await screen.findByText("Alice");
    expect(alice).toBeInTheDocument();
});

// 3. Mock function
it("calls onSelect", async () => {
    const user = userEvent.setup();
    const onSelect = vi.fn();

    render(<Options onSelect={onSelect} />);
    await user.click(screen.getByText("Option 1"));

    expect(onSelect).toHaveBeenCalledTimes(1);
});
```


### Mock API（MSW）

```tsx
// npm install -D msw

// test/mocks/handlers.ts
import { http, HttpResponse } from "msw";

export const handlers = [
    http.get("/api/users", () => {
        return HttpResponse.json([
            { id: 1, name: "Alice" },
            { id: 2, name: "Bob" }
        ]);
    })
];

// test/setup.ts
import { setupServer } from "msw/node";
import { handlers } from "./mocks/handlers";

const server = setupServer(...handlers);

beforeAll(() => server.listen());
afterEach(() => server.resetHandlers());
afterAll(() => server.close());

// Test 自動用 mock data
it("displays users from API", async () => {
    render(<UserList />);
    expect(await screen.findByText("Alice")).toBeInTheDocument();
});
```


### 測試 Custom Hook

```tsx
import { renderHook, act } from "@testing-library/react";

describe("useCounter", () => {
    it("increments", () => {
        const { result } = renderHook(() => useCounter(0));

        expect(result.current.count).toBe(0);

        act(() => {
            result.current.increment();
        });

        expect(result.current.count).toBe(1);
    });
});
```


### E2E Testing：Playwright

```bash
$ npm init playwright
```

```ts
// tests/login.spec.ts
import { test, expect } from "@playwright/test";

test("login flow", async ({ page }) => {
    await page.goto("/login");

    await page.fill('input[name="email"]', "alice@x.com");
    await page.fill('input[name="password"]', "password");
    await page.click('button[type="submit"]');

    await expect(page).toHaveURL("/dashboard");
});

// 真實瀏覽器
$ npx playwright test

// 2026 主流：Playwright（取代 Cypress）
```


### 測試心法

```text
1. Test behavior、不 test implementation
2. AAA pattern：Arrange / Act / Assert
3. 不測第三方
4. 快樂路徑 + 重要 error
5. 不要 mock 太多

2026 主流測試 stack：
- Vitest（unit / integration）
- Testing Library（render component）
- MSW（mock API）
- Playwright（E2E）

目標：80% coverage（不需要 100%）
```


**☕ 用人話講**

Testing 5 心法：(1) **Vitest + Testing Library**—2026 標配 (2) **Test like a user** (3) **getByRole 優於 getByTestId** (4) **MSW mock API** (5) **E2E 用 Playwright**。

RSC 是 React 最大革命—Server 跑 component、Client 只收 HTML。2026 Next.js App Router 預設。


### 傳統 React 的問題

```text
傳統 SPA：

1. 首屏白屏—載大 bundle
2. SEO 差—爬蟲看到空白 HTML
3. Waterfall—多層 useEffect 多輪請求
4. Bundle 大—所有 code 送 client
```


### RSC 解什麼

```text
Server Components：

1. Server 跑、回 HTML
   - 首屏快、SEO 好
   - 不送 component JS

2. 直接抓 DB
   - Component 內 await db.user.find()
   - 不用 API、不用 useEffect

3. 不送 component code
   - Bundle 小
   - lib 不在 client

4. 自動 streaming
   - 邊算邊送 HTML

只缺：沒 interactivity（用 Client Components）
```


### Server vs Client Component

```tsx
// app/page.tsx（Server Component 預設）
import { db } from "@/lib/db";

export default async function HomePage() {
    const users = await db.user.findMany();

    return (
        <div>
            <h1>Users</h1>
            <ul>
                {users.map(u => <li key={u.id}>{u.name}</li>)}
            </ul>
        </div>
    );
}

// Client Component（要互動）
"use client";

import { useState } from "react";

export default function Counter() {
    const [count, setCount] = useState(0);
    return (
        <button onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}>
            {count}
        </button>
    );
}
```


### Server + Client 組合

```tsx
// app/page.tsx（Server）
import { Counter } from "./Counter";   // Client component
import { db } from "@/lib/db";

export default async function HomePage() {
    const users = await db.user.findMany();

    return (
        <div>
            <h1>Users: {users.length}</h1>
            <ul>
                {users.map(u => <li key={u.id}>{u.name}</li>)}
            </ul>

            <Counter />
        </div>
    );
}

// Server：抓 users + render HTML
// Client：只 hydrate Counter
// Bundle 只包 Counter
```


### Server Component 限制

```text
不能用：
❌ useState / useEffect / useReducer
❌ onClick / onChange
❌ window / document / localStorage
❌ Browser-only library

能用：
✓ async / await
✓ DB 操作
✓ Server-only library（Prisma / fs）
✓ Environment variables
✓ Sensitive secrets

規則：
- 互動 → Client
- Data fetching → Server
- UI 渲染 → Server
```


### Server Actions

```tsx
// app/actions.ts
"use server";

import { db } from "@/lib/db";
import { revalidatePath } from "next/cache";

export async function createPost(formData: FormData) {
    const title = formData.get("title") as string;

    await db.post.create({
        data: { title, authorId: 1 }
    });

    revalidatePath("/posts");
}

// app/posts/new/page.tsx
import { createPost } from "../actions";

export default function NewPostPage() {
    return (
        <form action={createPost}>
            <input name="title" />
            <button type="submit">Create</button>
        </form>
    );
}

// 賣點：
// 1. 無 API endpoint
// 2. 無 JS 也能用
// 3. type-safe
// 4. 自動 revalidate
```


### useOptimistic（樂觀更新）

```tsx
"use client";

import { useOptimistic } from "react";
import { toggleLike } from "./actions";

export default function LikeButton({ post }) {
    const [optimisticLiked, addOptimistic] = useOptimistic(
        post.liked,
        (state, newValue: boolean) => newValue
    );

    const handleClick = async () => {
        addOptimistic(!optimisticLiked);
        await toggleLike(post.id);
    };

    return (
        <button onClick={handleClick}>
            {optimisticLiked ? "♥" : "♡"}
        </button>
    );
}

// 點下立刻變、不用等 server
// 失敗自動 rollback
```


### Streaming

```tsx
import { Suspense } from "react";

async function SlowComponent() {
    await sleep(3000);
    const data = await fetchSlowData();
    return <div>{data}</div>;
}

export default function Page() {
    return (
        <div>
            <h1>Page Title</h1>

            <Suspense fallback={<Spinner />}>
                <SlowComponent />
            </Suspense>

            <Footer />
        </div>
    );
}

// 1. 立刻 stream 標題 + footer
// 2. 慢 component 顯示 spinner
// 3. 載完 stream 出來
```


### RSC 心法

```text
2026 Next.js App Router 思路：

1. 預設 Server Component
2. 互動 leaf 用 "use client"
3. Server Action for mutation
4. Suspense 處理 loading
5. Revalidate for cache

2026 真實：
- 99% Next.js 新專案用 App Router
- 學會 RSC = 寫 modern React 標配
```


**🚀 進階技巧**

RSC 5 心法：(1) **預設 Server**—大部分 component 不需互動 (2) **"use client" leaf 化**—只互動部分標 (3) **Server Actions 取代 API**—type-safe mutation (4) **Suspense 處理 loading**—streaming UX (5) **revalidatePath / revalidateTag**—cache 同步。

